\\\\n   - support claim says what support covers;\\\\\\\\n   - visual contrast passes obvious manual inspection;\\\\\\\\n   - no custom CSS classes, no inline layout styles.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**6. Risk Notes**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nDo not change auth redirects, role resolution, Supabase client behavior, or RLS as part of this copy/layout fix. The trust panel is in the server page wrapper; auth mechanics live separately in `AuthEntryScreen` and `signUpAction`.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nBe careful with “бесплатно”: only claim what is definitely true. “Регистрация и заявка бесплатны” is safer than implying trips, guide services, or the whole platform are free.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nDo not promise “аккредитованные гиды” unless the product/data model actually enforces accreditation before guide marketplace participation. If enforcement is not complete, use “проверяем профиль и документы” until the guide verification flow is aligned.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nThe phone reuse concern belongs to the signup flow, not this visible panel. If addressed later, it may require product policy plus schema/action changes; do not casually add a phone unique constraint without normalization, backfill checks, duplicate handling, and a clear reason why shared family/business phones are disallowed.\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n\\\",\\\"exit_code\\\":0,\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"}}\\ndocs/qa/page-refactor-audit-2026-06-28/raw-results.json:28:    \\\"text\\\": \\\"«Проводник»\\\\nОткрытые группы\\\\nГотовые экскурсии\\\\nГиды\\\\nНаправления\\\\nКак это работает\\\\nСтать гидом\\\\nВойти\\\\nКуда отправимся?\\\\nКогда\\\\n≈\\\\n–\\\\nТемы\\\\nРусский\\\\nДетали\\\\nНайти гида\\\\n\\\\nБесплатно · без регистрации · гиды обычно отвечают в течение дня\\\\n\\\\nОткрытые группы\\\\nОткрытые группы\\\\nВсе группы\\\\nРоссия\\\\nМосква\\\\nЖдёт гида\\\\nСборная группа\\\\n· от 5 чел.\\\\n30 июня\\\\nГибкие даты\\\\n11:00–13:00\\\\nИстория и культура\\\\nГастрономия\\\\nП\\\\n+4\\\\n4 000 ₽ / чел\\\\nПрисоединиться\\\\nКраснодарский кра